{"id": "ChIJx5olsU7FwoARevXaC5zx6LY", "rating": 5, "userRatingCount": 9, "displayName": {"text": "Pinecone Bakeshop + Cafe", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJx5olsU7FwoARevXaC5zx6LY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tORlVtazVRemRtU200emMzRXdWM015YTFaRE1HYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Just went to the pre-open and it’s great! All the tarts were amazing. The varieties are well thought out and very unique flavors. My favorite was the peach earl grey tart, but I recommend getting a sampler of the small ones and picking your own favorite, but a large one of those to take home.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Just went to the pre-open and it’s great! All the tarts were amazing. The varieties are well thought out and very unique flavors. My favorite was the peach earl grey tart, but I recommend getting a sampler of the small ones and picking your own favorite, but a large one of those to take home.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kevin Sharpe", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112990077592574454851/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZ_mxlCD3jRVylv1zKB2IIbVOEEkm4K1Wz9_Nj4oMGE8PITTBf2g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-29T02:01:14.912762364Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tORlVtazVRemRtU200emMzRXdWM015YTFaRE1HYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tORlVtazVRemRtU200emMzRXdWM015YTFaRE1HYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c54eb1259ac7:0xb6e8f19c0bdaf57a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJx5olsU7FwoARevXaC5zx6LY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSa2RtY3dVbTl2TTE4NVVFcFllbDg1VFhCUlRHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Very comfy and cozy. Definitely is a place to have a cup of coffee and a piece of their unique flavor pie with friends.\n\nMy favorite is their mango sticky rice pie.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very comfy and cozy. Definitely is a place to have a cup of coffee and a piece of their unique flavor pie with friends.\n\nMy favorite is their mango sticky rice pie.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Helen Fong", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102467883630972889988/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIILhIkYg-0TYfUHHWUkRyMOc1JhkCmbTRZnHFRtcCkTYKdQGrP=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-30T00:03:21.823083179Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSa2RtY3dVbTl2TTE4NVVFcFllbDg1VFhCUlRHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSa2RtY3dVbTl2TTE4NVVFcFllbDg1VFhCUlRHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c54eb1259ac7:0xb6e8f19c0bdaf57a"}, {"name": "places/ChIJx5olsU7FwoARevXaC5zx6LY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toRVNFTTNTbEZZWmxwTGFEUTFOR0o0VldkM1ltYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a week ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Cute new cafe with awesome fruit tarts, matcha and coffee drinks, wonderful staff and great ambiance and design", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Cute new cafe with awesome fruit tarts, matcha and coffee drinks, wonderful staff and great ambiance and design", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jeremy Ho", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100976984624062910257/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIllmCf_kxKahos7KALivIr1BPAVWw0XmX51YAK1ugZKWfIgOY1=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-07-04T17:53:24.352197167Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toRVNFTTNTbEZZWmxwTGFEUTFOR0o0VldkM1ltYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com